<h1>Your password was changed</h1>

<p><strong><%= @name %>,</strong></p>

<p>
  Your password at <%= @website.name %> has been changed.
</p>

<p>
  If you requested this change, you do not need to do anything.
</p>

<p>
  If you did not request this change, please contact us and use the
  <%= link_to "forgot password", account_forgot_password_url(host: @website.domain, protocol: @website.scheme) %>
  feature on the website to reset your password.
</p>
